Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the entrance to the gulf,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:46.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,a Buddha statue, that's supposed to bring peace to the world, stands in ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:54.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that lies the port of immorality, Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From the overland entrance to town, there's always a noose,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:05.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,hanging for some unknown person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:11.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that lies the city of pleasure, Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:19.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At one time I was a businessman in Tokyo, now I'm a pirate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cheating bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Die you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dutch going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what Dutch does, when he's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curious types don't get popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:38.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much you paid for this, but it's worth less than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:45.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah i guess. So, the situation downtown in this place is the same too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:53.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, international villains run around here bashing horns. They all trick one another, from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not qualified to live, if all you can trust are your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's great while you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I may still be too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:12.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're so protected by their own independence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that I still don't know about their pasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You doing OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,International number 10013.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Send $120,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Under "Flyer's Company".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nice weather, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Chin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're pulling through somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:07.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,how long are you going to work with that Fry Face bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, Chin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That crazy Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:19.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that Ruskie got here, the market's been down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:24.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan's taken all the hotels rights, and the heroin routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a shred of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:33.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if they get the sea routes on top of that, we're dried out from head to ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is: Pull out, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some advice, Chin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even villains have sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:56.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When you shipped junk to the NPA, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:03.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\q1}It wasn't even close to a\N"no problem" situation, but who pulled out then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up the past like some old bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:16.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, at the very least, Balalaika has more honor than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ship your goods at our rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:25.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get second chances with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head to survive, Chin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drop some money onto us, from time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's inside your bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shipped them, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:06.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, that that torpedo boat was bought by some country bumpkin Russian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:12.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that they'll take jobs from pretty much anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This city sure has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The new board is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the pure, unadulterated, real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pure is a funny word to use in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just get it on the boat, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:42.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, our crew is so damn simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, sailor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:21.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to wash his face, but he's taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was Donnie Yen's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie Yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He gives us jobs from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:50.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're receiving a package from the Vietnamese military at Phu Quoc Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And since our schedule is open...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They say labor is to be respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do with all these pathetic jobs, Dutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:06.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder we can't get him out of these fucking white collar suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like wearing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with that Aloha shirt I got you at the market?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That ugly Aloha shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was some kind of punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I don't have taste?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they fell for the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's do or die from this point on, Luak-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've been down on your luck lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You fucked up the last hunt and got chased around by a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:58.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of this, and you get all the tolls between here and Kalimantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:26.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:29.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:39.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...desperately clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or aren't you trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:43.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A monkey could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hard on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never did this at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the raw materials research department.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I went on business trips, wrote reports...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:15.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...made phone calls, but I think being a subordinate was my real job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At night I had to deal with my superior's drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got my ass kicked once, when they were drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's fucked up, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgusting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Putting up with all that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You a masochist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Putting up with it is part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to be jobless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone survives like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,what did you do before coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:51.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I do hasn't changed from then to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:58.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you were going wild at the river, swinging around a cutlass, as a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:06.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I stole, I killed, and did all sorts of bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was beyond fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, we've got several boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You better pray, Dutch, so you know which heaven you're going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any merchants around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate's bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you find out what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're small and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's either cops looking for pirates or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, it's a Red Alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Passing right by yellow, straight to a red lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming at 28 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Benny'll explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:21.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's three more. A total of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:26.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first three started accelerating from the island we just passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:31.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The three on port side came from behind a different island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Changing course to the left is dangerous, the ones there will get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same with the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A basic hunting pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're fast too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks all the way up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:55.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the stink of blood and smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're being targeted by pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, what's the background of our client?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That observation hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:13.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been neglecting checks on Donnie Yen's financial situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Can you hear me, Lagoon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. It's been a while, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:20.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Luak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no prey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, before you get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's prey right here, Beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An old torpedo boat, with a nice wingspan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Six on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Luak, he brought everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, all these bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Chin get you on this, Luak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God must feel sorry for your stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:50.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have a pint of lead in you, maybe you'll shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's got us on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But these positions, Dutch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Rock. Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:11.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:18.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's common sense to position yourselves out of each other's line of fire. Amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you right to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They still have four ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, they're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:31.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:32.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Hand's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make them dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:52.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, take a break from talking about your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I need to concentrate on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's two on the left, and two more to the right, behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And one more right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the shit on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance the jitterbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She jumped ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see with the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot an ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her! Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:48.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:54.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which ship is she on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's on her fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the third is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her! Kill her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:25.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. My ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:33.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one who ended up dancing with hot lead was you, Luak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:44.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not dealing with those demons anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. She did it all herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said that out loud, but I thought something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what broke to make her like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:14.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I must be broken too, if I'm standing here praising her destructiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Luak fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:24.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot. I'd like to see what his mother's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He shoved a burner up my ass, before he croaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to kill that Luak bastard all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moving out so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Such hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we help, Chin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:03.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must have something mistaken. It's a pathetic rumor running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:08.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we sit down and discuss it over lunch, we'll get it sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, you piece of horse-shit, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:20.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got nothing to ask you. We know all we want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you can do, while you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. We busted our asses for nothing. So damn stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. It's just like being bitten by a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all right, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets aren't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Lagoon Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Japonski! It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Dutch around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Balalaika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you went on a goose chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you got stuck playing with Chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He told me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit too loud to conspire about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told the other groups in the area what was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was dead from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure this doesn't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pain for you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even need aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dutch. It's not much of a return...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll let you hear something amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What they call "Pleasure and Pain".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cooler than J.B.?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a job for you soon. I'll call you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a call about a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:50.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She told me some gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, Rock, do you have somewhere to go after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maintenance on the electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the mental anguish incurred due to external interference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:13.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,as your employer, it is my duty to provide entertainment as compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:20.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I propose a trip to the Yellow Flag, to drink away our pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can go till dawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, it's decided! Get the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:33.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, it's not a job. Wear that Aloha shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:20.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, there are fights that you must still take on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Prepare the submerging torpedo ship.
